HEADWORD: dominated
<hw>dominated</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>controlled or ruled
by superior authority or power.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> dominated by, under the thumb
of(predicate).</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>controlled by one's wife; -- of men.</def>⟦br⟧
